<p class="text-intro">(Adapted from:  Ontario Ministry of Education. The Ontario Curriculum Grades 9 and 10: Mathematics, 2005. p. 6.)</p> </p><section class="zero numbers"></ul></section></div><aside class="zero main__sidebar"></aside></div></div> </a> </div></div><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></section>









